      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's not just being lonely. it's like the person who made me real is gone. i look in the mirror and i don't even recognize the person looking back. i'm just performing these tasks, eating, sleeping, breathing... but it all feels so incredibly heavy and meaningless. like i'm just waiting for something to happen that'll never happen.",
